LEX Escrow


"Payer" is person

"Seller" is person

"Arbiter" is person

"Amount" is amount


The Payer pays Amount into escrow, appoints the Seller, appoints the Arbiter


CLAUSE: Pay Out

The Arbiter may pay the escrow to the Seller


CLAUSE: Pay Back

The Arbiter may pay the escrow to the Payer


